Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna sing something funny and then you I want you to say get lost bum. Oh my god is love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All I got is love you say get lost bum. Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, baby, all I got is the love. All I got is love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't got nothing but love honey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd have fun with that one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I can't give you anything but love baby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost. Oh get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If all love is all I can afford get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's funny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get people a chance get back from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The bookstore and things I know everybody I don't know if everyone got
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Through everything. It looks like quite a few are here. So I guess we'll go ahead and start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And please no video taping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No video taping and turn off your cell phones if you caught someone on the break, please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have complaints every lecture because of that so I have to announce it after every break we take
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people forget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of life now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cell phone cell phones are connected to our ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much again, we appreciate you coming and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave and I would
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope that you carry on our work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that what we have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought to you that you remember and teach others
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing the doctors teachings on love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason deals with particulars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas love deals with holes and essence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplishes great feats because of its purity of motive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,love takes no position and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,inclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,love augments the positive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,focuses on life's goodness in all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,David yes, when you say that love takes no position
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is meant by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you love them if they do do this and you love them if they don't or
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a primary is a primary in my my personal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions are irrelevant if you've decided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain situation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they hoot and say your you're terrible. You still love them because they're so dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody doesn't think I'm the greatest needs help
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a mother's love is unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,remember as a kindergarten or a first grader
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We wore long stockings when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Long stockings in the wintertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, we wore long stockings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to school, and that day I had diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was one unholy mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Long socks and diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody had to clean me up when I got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I remember being told,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,don't feel bad about it, you couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't not only the cleaning me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but the relief of my guilt that I had done such a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So we bless others by our forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that in a certain way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody can help being other than they,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,considering the world situation at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Hitler did what he thought was the most necessary thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine attempts to kill him all failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so even with Adolf Hitler, I say he was dedicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought he was being of service by what he did, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did the same thing in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the kamikaze pilots are doing what they think they should do for their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though they're trying to kill us and bomb us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not hate the kamikaze pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I respected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I respected kamikaze pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Willing to give up their life for their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought that's,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I respected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tell a funny story about diarrhea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tell a funny story about diarrhea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,David had a little bout with an intestinal bug here about two weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we kept talking about this problem he was having with diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have an African Grey, and she picked it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and now she runs around saying diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parrot says diarrhea, diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he's telling this story just now about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but think of broccoli going diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say anything in front of our African Grey parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The parrot will pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything you say, you better be prepared to hear it back for another 50 times, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Including phone numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And credit card numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this bird is sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I got so I'd go in the other room to place a mail order,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, by phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know she's going to remember the credit card number
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and start blabbing it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got all but the last four digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the African Grey parrot is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So each being in an African Grey parrot is very much a being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Each being I love and respect for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they bring joy to our life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's part of having them with us, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the joy they bring to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when they're being bad, they still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you're being bad, I love you still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At 3 o'clock this morning, we have a white kitty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's my little stinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he went tearing through the house several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and he runs the whole length of the hallway into the bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,around the bed, and back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this morning, at about 3 in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he was doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I grabbed the water bottle I keep by the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and sprayed him to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets, just once in a while, not all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have three kitties, three kitties and one doggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like us talking about our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By level 500, approximately 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of people experience happiness as a basic quality of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With spiritual intention, love becomes a way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity for love is limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The more one loves, the more one can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my sweetie pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say something about the capacity for love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love, the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a non-physical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it's non-physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite love of Almighty God is the ultimate expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is discovered that to be loving is also to be lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love appears in the animal kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the birdsong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the dog's wagging tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitty's purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Love uplifts others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is present everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Its presence only needs to be realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The teaching of Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was essentially to avoid negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of his teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was for his followers to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want to ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't expect anything when given?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it has become what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have become loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have no limitations or demands
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on people out there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that they should be this way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You love them no matter how they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they're obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you feel sorry for the criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that they didn't know any other lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that their life was so pathetic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is all they had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Run down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and grab the lady's purse
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as they run down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught people how to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught people how to handle a robber, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you do is you take your money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you take your money
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you throw it on this side of the sidewalk
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you run that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will go for the money
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Always give the robber your billfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people when they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when they say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they may say that they're being unconditionally loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's always a hidden agenda behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's always a hidden agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if I do this for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they will love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then they'll react like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that's why I wanted you to clarify
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love for whatever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're stupid enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stupid and obnoxious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional love is given without attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Without requirements, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no strings attached
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You become lovable when you are loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The more loving we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the more lovable we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my dog knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog loves me a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say she loves us both very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that we got that unconditional love down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's so much out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used as kind of a flippant term anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to describe love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I wanted to clarify that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's with no strings attached,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,not to expect anything back when given, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there's no coffee in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She would never get me up without coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ knew that at the level of unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the soul's destiny was certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is taught by the world's great religions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,such as Lotus Land Buddhism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Diagnostic differential between infatuation versus love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Infatuation, passion, and attraction calibrate at 145,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas love calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The locus of infatuation is the self with a small S, the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The locus of love is self with a large S, or the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The origin of infatuation is the animal instinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas the origin of love is a spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The mental function of infatuation is impaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's uplifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of infatuation is to mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's to bond and to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The duration of infatuation is transitory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas love is permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotions of infatuation are in excess and imbalance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotions are calm and balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain physiology of infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the left brain, the physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the right brain, the etheric.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional process of infatuation is frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,frantic, fearful, tormented,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's gratitude, peaceful, self-fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stability in infatuation is desperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's enhanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Body functions in infatuation are impaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,loss of appetite, loss of sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The description of infatuation is craving,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's contentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathology in infatuation is suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,despair, stalking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, there's well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgment in infatuation is impaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception in infatuation is exaggerated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas in love, it's illuminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of infatuation is to possess,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to own, to control, to capture,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Productivity in infatuation is disrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's enhanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The self-image in infatuation is inflated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Balance in infatuation is erratic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The hormone and endocrine in infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is adrenaline and the sex hormones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, they are endorphins and oxytocin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The social image in infatuation is inflated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's enhanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellectual function in infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is to romanticize and lower mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's realistic and higher mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness in infatuation lowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it raises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The style of infatuation is involvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,horizontal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's alignment and vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to say something about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the horizontal and the vertical?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That when you're in love, it's vertical,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you're lying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When there is, when there's,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's involvement, you're horizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because that's the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,between an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,An attachment is something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're attached to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you're aligned to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You might even kill them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so attached to her that I had to kill her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when I started flirting with somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So alignment means that your purposes are aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why a spiritual overall field in a relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a relationship ensures its longevity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the positive effect it has on others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you become an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love, the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes love is misconceived as an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment is one thing and love is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can love something and either be attached
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or not be attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Relatedness in infatuation is demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's harmonious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of infatuation is to satisfy and to own,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The pattern of infatuation is individualism,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas with love, it's concordance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Loss is experienced in infatuation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with depression, rage, hate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas loss is experienced in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with grief and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego dynamics of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity for love increases
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as positionalities are surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a quality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and emerges in accord with spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,be kind to everything and everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,including oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times with no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Love illuminates the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.75,0:22:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the lovability of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because it opens the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind thinks and argues
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and carries on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But the heart just continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So even when you're very, very bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or your thoughts would tell you one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but the heart would tell you something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind could be critical
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and disagree,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but the heart is loving no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the heart does not put any conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,on what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the mind does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart, I love you no matter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,whether there's coffee in the morning or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:24:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Love makes no demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending level 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A key to making love unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,events and people are recontextualized
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as simply, quote, limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,not bad or unlovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.38,0:24:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness ensues from the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of humility to surrender the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and its events to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray to the Holy Spirit for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.86,0:24:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the truth about the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.86,0:24:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrender all perceptual positionalities
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.38,0:25:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and their egoistic gain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the revelation of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.38,0:25:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,pray to the Holy Spirit for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the truth about a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.00,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.00,0:25:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are we to forgive that person
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if there was a conflict?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.16,0:25:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or just accept them for what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.16,0:25:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.16,0:25:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're still seeing them the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.16,0:25:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or you wouldn't be forgiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.58,0:25:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the course of miracles, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.13,0:25:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but not as a consequence of how you're seeing it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because you may still see it the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.57,0:25:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when I ask for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.64,0:25:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surrendering my perception
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.64,0:25:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.64,0:26:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.64,0:26:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's transformed,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that it still is lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that somebody I'm angry at
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.83,0:26:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot help but be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.83,0:26:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So now instead of hating them or being angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.93,0:26:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.93,0:26:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, it's too bad
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.93,0:26:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that they can't see it the way I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.93,0:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Because I know their life is painful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.93,0:26:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the way they are seeing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.93,0:26:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they see it my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.02,0:26:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the world stops being painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.02,0:26:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.02,0:26:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.13,0:26:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.39,0:26:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,this domain is one of maximum spiritual opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.39,0:26:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with a multitude of options
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.39,0:26:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which aid the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.39,0:26:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, one can be grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.39,0:26:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of resentful about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.39,0:26:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.25,0:27:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rare is it to be born a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.50,0:27:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarer still,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to have heard of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And even rarer still,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.50,0:27:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to pursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.60,0:27:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.60,0:27:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,words that describe this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.60,0:27:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 0.4% of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.60,0:27:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,miraculous, inclusive,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.71,0:27:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,inner joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.71,0:27:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.71,0:27:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,non-selective,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.71,0:27:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.71,0:27:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,merciful,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.71,0:27:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.71,0:27:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.71,0:27:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.71,0:27:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.71,0:27:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,selfless,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.71,0:27:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.71,0:27:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,synchronicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.71,0:27:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,radiant,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.71,0:27:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,siddhis,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.71,0:27:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.71,0:27:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,effortless,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.71,0:27:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,patience,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.71,0:27:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,unlimited,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.71,0:27:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,persistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.71,0:27:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,emerging Self with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.71,0:28:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,diffuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.71,0:28:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,devotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.71,0:28:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,openness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.71,0:28:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,saintly,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.71,0:28:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,rapture,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.71,0:28:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.11,0:28:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wowzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.79,0:28:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love, joy, and ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.02,0:28:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As love becomes unconditional,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.02,0:28:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to be experienced as inner joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.02,0:28:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy arises from within each moment of existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.41,0:28:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,not from any outer source.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.67,0:28:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The hallmark of this state is compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.67,0:28:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.67,0:28:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,people have a notable effect on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.67,0:28:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,David, when you say that you experience joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.32,0:28:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what type of joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or when you say joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.19,0:29:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.19,0:29:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy is, to me, not just an emotional thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.36,0:29:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy may occur as an emotion along with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.66,0:29:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but joy is like,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you thought the dog was run over and killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.13,0:29:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.13,0:29:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that it was only hurt a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.13,0:29:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's still living,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.13,0:29:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and its tail wags,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and your heart just jumps with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.07,0:29:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The doggie's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.07,0:29:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,not really badly hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you jump with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.35,0:29:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You jump with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.35,0:29:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump with joy when I get up every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.35,0:29:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.35,0:29:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At my age,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.35,0:29:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you're glad to see yourself in the mirror every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.35,0:29:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dave, how are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.35,0:30:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy arises within each moment of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.69,0:30:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It says joy arises from within each moment of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.69,0:30:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.69,0:30:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not dependent on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.69,0:30:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the audience laughs or not is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they're enjoying what I'm saying is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.69,0:30:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.88,0:30:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To be self-sufficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.88,0:30:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because the radiance of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.88,0:30:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,love is everywhere present.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.88,0:30:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the sun just shining everywhere on the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.20,0:30:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.74,0:30:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.74,0:30:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything happens effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.79,0:31:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,by synchronicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.85,0:31:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One sees the world and everything in it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.85,0:31:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to be an expression of love and divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.00,0:31:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This state is impersonal, not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.80,0:31:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It represents the power of the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.80,0:31:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,not of the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.80,0:31:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the capacity to love many people simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Love has no limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.31,0:31:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The more people you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.31,0:31:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.81,0:31:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.48,0:31:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love is the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the majority of spiritually committed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.48,0:31:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love at 540
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.82,0:31:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is a practical and reachable goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.82,0:31:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.07,0:32:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is reachable by very simple means.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.07,0:32:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.07,0:32:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.07,0:32:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to live with care and kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.07,0:32:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on a daily basis without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.38,0:32:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of us would like to give that example
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.85,0:32:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of living with care and kindness on a daily basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.85,0:32:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we try to apply it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.85,0:32:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it just doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.85,0:32:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you give us some tips
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.85,0:32:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as to how we can achieve that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.85,0:32:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because of how we are viewing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.04,0:32:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when we place expectations on the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then we set ourselves up for disruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.04,0:32:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I have no expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.55,0:32:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that there will be coffee in the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.55,0:32:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have great hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.55,0:32:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It may or may not be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.83,0:33:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.83,0:33:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have great hopes that when we get home today,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.05,0:33:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the doggie will not have had an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.05,0:33:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if doggie had an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.92,0:33:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So unconditionally loving means
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.51,0:33:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,no conditions, no conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.28,0:33:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the way that I am
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.28,0:33:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the way the world has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.28,0:33:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The doggie doesn't have to be the way I want her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.28,0:33:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would prefer it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.28,0:33:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's only a doggie,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.28,0:33:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she's got to go wah-wah,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.35,0:33:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,she's going to go wah-wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.74,0:33:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully not before we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.75,0:33:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.75,0:33:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.11,0:33:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.11,0:33:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a silent nonverbal benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.31,0:33:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of being in the actual presence
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.31,0:33:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of such a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.31,0:34:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The silent transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.89,0:34:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the high frequency energy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.89,0:34:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher's aura
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.88,0:34:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is referred to as the silent teaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the transmission of no mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.50,0:34:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the grace of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.76,0:34:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The benediction of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and is not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the transmission of grace
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.44,0:34:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.69,0:34:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which radiates forth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.26,0:34:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.26,0:34:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The grace of the guru, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.32,0:34:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when we did the calibration on this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.32,0:34:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if that was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, we both kind of said,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.32,0:34:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, that's,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.32,0:34:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone had to be
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.51,0:34:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the presence of a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.51,0:35:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean to be in your,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.51,0:35:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,any teacher's presence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.51,0:35:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Buddha transmitted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.51,0:35:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.51,0:35:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.51,0:35:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's giving them a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.34,0:35:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's symbolic of the transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.34,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To have been in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.07,0:35:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of a great teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.07,0:35:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The most beneficial thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that can happen to you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.28,0:35:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is to have been in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.28,0:35:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of a great teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.28,0:35:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because you pick up the vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.63,0:35:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which cannot be taught
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,via words or lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.48,0:35:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.78,0:35:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hopeful that it could
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.78,0:35:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,be transmitted otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.78,0:35:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.80,0:35:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You pick up the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.84,0:35:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by the physical presence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,within the aura, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:36:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it lasts a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.75,0:36:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teachers that I have
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.73,0:36:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,encountered in my lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.73,0:36:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already incorporated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.73,0:36:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,into my brain function,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.73,0:36:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.28,0:36:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So then it is worthwhile
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.19,0:36:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to go from long distance
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.19,0:36:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to see a teacher that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.19,0:36:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,would have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.19,0:36:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.38,0:36:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the people we see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.38,0:36:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,any seekers,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.38,0:36:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,travel long distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.38,0:36:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.38,0:36:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from Australia and South America
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.38,0:36:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and Africa and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.38,0:36:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And all they want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.69,0:36:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is pick up the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.69,0:36:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.15,0:36:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when they go
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.15,0:36:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,home, they bring it back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.15,0:36:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.15,0:36:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So they come from all
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.69,0:36:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,different countries
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.69,0:36:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.69,0:36:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel greatly honored
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.07,0:36:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by their request to grant
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.19,0:37:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever their request may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.19,0:37:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.07,0:37:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been requested
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.71,0:37:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to go certain places
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.71,0:37:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world because what
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.71,0:37:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they wanted was my energy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that country that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.11,0:37:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all is questioning us to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.11,0:37:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we went there,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.11,0:37:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was just for our energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.11,0:37:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just for our energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.13,0:37:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.13,0:37:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want your energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,South Korea, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.05,0:37:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.09,0:37:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.11,0:37:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, all right, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.07,0:37:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.07,0:37:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to South Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.07,0:37:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and be able to be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.07,0:37:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We prevented a war
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.15,0:37:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from happening there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.15,0:37:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of our having been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.15,0:37:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.15,0:37:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.15,0:37:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.15,0:37:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So how long does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.15,0:37:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you carry that aura
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.15,0:37:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.15,0:37:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifetimes, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.23,0:38:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you carry that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.23,0:38:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry it for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.23,0:38:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I carry it for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.61,0:38:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.61,0:38:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you become that,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.28,0:38:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you yourself
