Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.55,0:38:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.55,0:38:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your universal lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.55,0:39:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So being unconditionally loving
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.46,0:39:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of existing,
