Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.82,0:43:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,o'clock anybody who tries to escape we've notified the police god bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:44:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all I love you so much too much loving you fall over I almost fell over and be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.98,0:44:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your fault what happens next we're gonna do any question oh okay oh okay now if
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.44,0:44:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll talk into the mic
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.61,0:44:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,okay my question my doctors have not been able to give me a diagnosis I have
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.86,0:44:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,had this condition for 10 years but this allows me not to accept a label I've
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.05,0:44:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,been studying your work and also a course in miracles I'm addressing the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.61,0:45:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,physical mental and spiritual aspects of this would you tell me if I continue to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.51,0:45:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,try and raise my calibration can I heal the body or is this a karmic death for
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.90,0:45:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.19,0:45:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.46,0:45:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,, well I wouldn't differentiate between the two everything is both what's your
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,question whether this is karmic this karmic I have no diagnosis from doctors
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.82,0:45:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic or what or whether this is some kind of physical physical that she can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.26,0:45:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,heal oh this is something that she can heal resist Wow this is something she can heal wow this is something she can heal wow this is something she can heal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.38,0:46:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was physical therapy plus intense spiritual work okay better get better
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.42,0:46:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what's up doc she you one last time I struggled to let go of guilt specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.15,0:46:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt around sexual behavior this is not very
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.55,0:46:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,good
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.32,0:46:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing is going in these lights really in my eyes right I'm having
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.32,0:46:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,blinded and deaf other than that I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.07,0:46:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than being blind and deaf, I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.03,0:46:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, make it brief so she can relate it to me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.36,0:46:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like some tips on letting go of guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.32,0:46:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and a sense of wrongness for particularly sexual guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.25,0:47:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, no matter how much work I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.05,0:47:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.92,0:47:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets deeper and deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.21,0:47:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a sense that...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.67,0:47:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a problem with sexual addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.48,0:47:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, give me the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.26,0:47:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He can undo the sexual guilt by forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.61,0:47:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for his limitation of being the victim of his gonads.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.07,0:47:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell him the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.42,0:47:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell him the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.59,0:47:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The solution is the removal of the gonads.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.36,0:47:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.19,0:47:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you would be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.53,0:47:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.69,0:47:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be willing to do that, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.23,0:47:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get back to you on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.96,0:48:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's drawing the line there, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.38,0:48:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I get stuck out of my body much of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.13,0:48:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering if you can teach us something
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.26,0:48:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that would allow us to learn how to stay in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.98,0:48:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You do what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.07,0:48:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an experience where I feel like I get stuck out of my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.71,0:48:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering if Dr. Hawkins would teach us
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.17,0:48:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,something that would help me learn how to stay in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.90,0:48:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.90,0:48:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels that he gets stuck out of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.57,0:48:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which is opposite than everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.28,0:48:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wants you to have, is there something
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.73,0:48:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can tell him to stay in the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.94,0:48:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's having experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.38,0:48:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he go out of the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.76,0:48:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you go out of the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.32,0:48:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.78,0:48:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, does it happen spontaneously?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.26,0:48:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.40,0:48:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hemming and hawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.30,0:48:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you go out of the body spontaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.46,0:48:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it something that you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.67,0:49:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not something I'm conscious of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.84,0:49:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You just go out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.84,0:49:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's your complaint about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.25,0:49:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.25,0:49:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It does seem that way sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.40,0:49:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I associate a lot of experience of suffering with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.53,0:49:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with the way I feel when I'm like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.53,0:49:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.53,0:49:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He experiences suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.53,0:49:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,like he relates suffering to that when he's out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.53,0:49:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because it's against his will?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.07,0:49:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because it's against your will that you feel the suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.26,0:49:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people study and spend all kinds of money
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.78,0:49:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,learning how to leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.78,0:49:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.09,0:49:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.09,0:49:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.57,0:49:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.71,0:49:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more about, I guess, functioning in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.71,0:49:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, as long as I'm trying to function in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.71,0:50:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.71,0:50:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to function in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.67,0:50:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.67,0:50:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And he can't because he keeps going into this outer body,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.67,0:50:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this outer body experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.48,0:50:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go out of body,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.48,0:50:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what does your body do while you're out of the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.61,0:50:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sitting in a chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.88,0:50:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and you go out of body,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.07,0:50:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.07,0:50:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the body just stay sitting in the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.26,0:50:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, but it's, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.26,0:50:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my ability to function is,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.26,0:50:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels inhibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.26,0:50:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.26,0:50:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His ability to function is impaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.32,0:50:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.94,0:50:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I work,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.94,0:50:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working in restaurants recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.94,0:50:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He works in a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.94,0:50:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.80,0:50:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this happen while you're at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.34,0:50:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.34,0:50:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.96,0:51:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it stress-related?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.01,0:51:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.03,0:51:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you fall over?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.03,0:51:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when you say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.03,0:51:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.03,0:51:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of, it's like, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.11,0:51:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.11,0:51:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,straining to use my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.11,0:51:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or to think, or to feel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.11,0:51:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.78,0:51:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's straining to think or to feel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.78,0:51:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.78,0:51:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's straining?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.78,0:51:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's straining to think or feel things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.78,0:51:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,when he's out of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.78,0:51:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it won't function.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.78,0:51:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The body won't function.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.53,0:51:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.53,0:51:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You just leave it where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.53,0:51:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If my body goes to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.53,0:51:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.53,0:51:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and wait till it wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.17,0:51:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, to follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.36,0:51:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow what the body's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.36,0:51:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.36,0:51:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He should adjust himself to what the,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.36,0:51:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he thinks the body is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.36,0:51:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.36,0:51:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.36,0:51:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.40,0:51:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.40,0:51:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should adjust yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.40,0:51:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to what the body is doing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.40,0:51:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.40,0:51:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.63,0:51:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.78,0:52:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.78,0:52:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.94,0:52:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, we don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.94,0:52:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.94,0:52:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes too much time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.94,0:52:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have so many people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.94,0:52:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that are asking questions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.40,0:52:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.69,0:52:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.69,0:52:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.42,0:52:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.42,0:52:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.78,0:52:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.78,0:52:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Veritas Pub actually helped me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.78,0:52:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pick out the color of the shirt for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.78,0:52:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.78,0:52:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It says,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.78,0:52:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,trust me, I'm,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.78,0:52:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.78,0:52:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.78,0:52:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.96,0:52:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you could wear it while watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.96,0:52:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.96,0:52:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.96,0:52:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you could wear it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.96,0:52:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,watching Animal Planet
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.96,0:52:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with Susan on the couch or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.96,0:52:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I like,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.96,0:52:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.96,0:52:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.05,0:52:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.05,0:52:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.05,0:52:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.05,0:52:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could explain to me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.05,0:52:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'm three,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.05,0:52:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.05,0:52:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm doing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.51,0:52:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.51,0:53:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.51,0:53:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.51,0:53:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you go about surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.76,0:53:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.76,0:53:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you quit trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.51,0:53:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.51,0:53:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight, fight, fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.51,0:53:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm gonna surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.09,0:53:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.71,0:53:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That means letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.71,0:53:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.57,0:53:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.57,0:53:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it means acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.44,0:53:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.44,0:53:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the fact that,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.73,0:53:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.73,0:53:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm old and ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.73,0:53:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.73,0:53:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I blame it on God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.73,0:53:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.73,0:53:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.73,0:53:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to look like a fish and swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.73,0:53:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.73,0:53:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wanted me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.73,0:53:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to have wings and fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.28,0:53:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.28,0:53:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wants to be old
