Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.75,1:21:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel a very profound, pure, unconditional love coming from those.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.35,1:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that reminds me of the statement of Krishna that says,
