Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.28,1:22:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get kind of confused, so we can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.67,1:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.77,1:22:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to ask for a blessing.
