Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.57,1:22:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.93,1:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you in the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.35,1:22:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.56,1:23:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to ask how not to doubt, doubt of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.00,1:23:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do prayer and the same thing everybody does.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.30,1:23:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, please help me to understand my relationship to thee and thy infinite nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.96,1:23:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just with prayer and supplication.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.76,1:23:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And going to church or whatever devotional activities are part of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.23,1:23:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.22,1:23:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Service to the poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.11,1:23:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Service to the sick and dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.39,1:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's miracles every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.72,1:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to slow down enough to recognize them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.02,1:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.30,1:23:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To be aware of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.52,1:23:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.56,1:23:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a friend now who's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.36,1:23:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray every day to God for the alleviation of this person's illness and their recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.55,1:23:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.81,1:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to their karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.22,1:24:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.07,1:24:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.00,1:24:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.97,1:24:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please bless my mother?
