Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.14,1:24:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.06,1:24:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.89,1:24:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.89,1:24:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Veronica.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.68,1:24:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Veronica?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.47,1:24:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.98,1:24:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And she has cirrhosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.13,1:24:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cirrhosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.97,1:24:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.32,1:24:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to pray for her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.72,1:24:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray to thee, O Lord, for her mother's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.42,1:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.03,1:24:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.39,1:24:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. O'Keefe and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.59,1:24:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.36,1:24:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bless my parents and my family?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.36,1:25:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bless his family?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.01,1:25:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.43,1:25:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to bless his family.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.52,1:25:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.03,1:25:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.50,1:25:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.11,1:25:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.38,1:25:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.84,1:25:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.47,1:25:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.14,1:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.96,1:25:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop, hop, hop, hop.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.06,1:25:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.35,1:25:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't be able to record it if you're not talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.10,1:25:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.14,1:25:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.77,1:25:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're discussing logistics.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.14,1:25:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,During the lecture and through teaching, talking about being loving to everyone, including ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.00,1:25:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in an environment that seemed to tend to have me repress anger, emotions,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.93,1:25:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and so it would come out sideways a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.18,1:26:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any suggestions for the better, more loving ways,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.22,1:26:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or the most loving way to process out those emotional things that seem to be in my body?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.30,1:26:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not in your body.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.05,1:26:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.81,1:26:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in your memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.25,1:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you remember angriness, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.90,1:26:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.47,1:26:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thing is to forgive it and let it be that that was their karma, that was their way of being,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.43,1:26:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.09,1:26:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't think about it around the clock seven days a week, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.13,1:26:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, and I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.86,1:26:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even as much the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.72,1:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in a situation, you run into a person, that stranger on the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.71,1:26:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what if they, like if I'm by myself, I can detach from the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.32,1:26:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, I'm in a car, and the person cuts you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.47,1:27:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can realize I'm angry, but I'm not really angry at them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.50,1:27:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I get confronted, it's been those times in my life that everybody loves Troy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.69,1:27:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,except those times when Troy flips.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.50,1:27:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.96,1:27:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He just says it's a split reaction.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.72,1:27:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like a knee-jerk reaction when he goes off.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.39,1:27:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.93,1:27:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he's trying to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.55,1:27:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to avoid normal human emotions?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.47,1:27:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is there a more loving way to...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.56,1:27:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To approach it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.50,1:27:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ignore it when it happens, it feels like I'm not loving myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.00,1:27:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stuff it down, I feel like I'm not loving myself by getting it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.69,1:27:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.43,1:27:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not loving to...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.93,1:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just get mad at a person?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.46,1:27:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.76,1:27:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, someone cuts you off. That makes me mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.71,1:27:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just get mad and be done with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.85,1:27:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to be the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.09,1:28:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.43,1:28:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.92,1:28:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't become violent.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.77,1:28:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be normal and don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.18,1:28:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.11,1:28:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I'm sorry that I lost my temper. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.89,1:28:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.77,1:28:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God don't care anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.64,1:28:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were created as a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.53,1:28:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.88,1:28:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.46,1:28:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me that all fear is an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.68,1:28:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all fear an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.06,1:28:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all fear an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.25,1:28:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.85,1:28:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you had a fear, should you confront it and address it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.68,1:28:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.61,1:28:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.64,1:29:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If all fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.22,1:29:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.78,1:29:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Level.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.98,1:29:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.39,1:29:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're karmically destined and nothing is going to make it any...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.72,1:29:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, depending on your level of spiritual reality, your level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.60,1:29:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll either be affected by it or not affected by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.19,1:29:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've transcended it, you won't be asking the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.17,1:29:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.01,1:29:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.11,1:29:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.72,1:29:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll take one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.89,1:29:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.65,1:29:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.81,1:29:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.27,1:29:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it short.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.94,1:29:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I got four people up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.44,1:29:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.22,1:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.39,1:29:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.06,1:29:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we get your grace?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.85,1:29:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.10,1:29:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They want your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.13,1:29:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.43,1:29:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.98,1:29:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.09,1:29:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They want your grace?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.64,1:30:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.25,1:30:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.14,1:30:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.06,1:30:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.21,1:30:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.98,1:30:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They want something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.56,1:30:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.25,1:30:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.05,1:30:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.18,1:30:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, God bless you in the name of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.90,1:30:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.65,1:30:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.05,1:30:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.10,1:30:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to take a quick break and then we're going to do testimonials.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.07,1:30:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll have you line up on this side for testimonials.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.14,1:30:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
